  "detailed_description": "<h1>If you like prologue add full version to wishlist</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/Przechwytywanie.PNG?t=1620669585\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCRAPNAUT : PROLOGUE</h2>Scrapnaut: Prologue is a free demo version of the game Scrapnaut. Try it yourself for free!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.poster.avif?t=1620669585\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.webm?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/8c39f17c60370764fa55d22f32460f1e.mp4?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create your own farm and produce food. Use your cooking pot and discover different types of meals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.poster.avif?t=1620669585\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.webm?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/9433375c515c82541843d2f68d972d6e.mp4?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect the necessary resources to build your base, fix damaged items and complete quests. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/faf14dcf697976e5de4026f1a4a64843.poster.avif?t=1620669585\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/faf14dcf697976e5de4026f1a4a64843.webm?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/faf14dcf697976e5de4026f1a4a64843.mp4?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build and improve your bases! Produce and store electrical energy. Be prepared for enemy raids! Each biome allows you to build various unique items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/a91c0ab9a475f93b18504822df17ed93.poster.avif?t=1620669585\" width=570 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/a91c0ab9a475f93b18504822df17ed93.webm?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391220/extras/a91c0ab9a475f93b18504822df17ed93.mp4?t=1620669585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create and improve your equipment. A good weapon and armor will help you survive, but when your opponent is much stronger than you - better run away!",
